fields.name: Expert Handling
fields.ai_description: When you perform a Barrel Roll action, remove 1 enemy Target Lock from your ship.

fields.name: Elusive
fields.ai_description: When defending, the attacker must reroll one Crit or Hit result. You cannot use this ability if you are stressed.

fields.name: Stealth Device
fields.ai_description: Increase your agility value by 1. If you are hit by an attack, this ability ceases.

fields.name: Shield Upgrade
fields.ai_description: Increase your Shield value by 1

fields.name: Stygium Array
fields.description: After you decloak, you may perform an Evade action. At the start of the End Phase, you may spend 1 evade token to gain 1 cloak token.

fields.name: Autothrusters
fields.description: After you perform an action, you may perform a red Barrel Roll or red Boost action.
fields.ai_description: When defending, if you are beyond range 2 or outside the attacker's primary arc, change 1 of your blank results to an Evade result.

fields.name: Whisper
fields.ai_description: After you perform an attack that hits, gain 1 Focus token.

fields.name: Dark Curse
fields.ai_description: While you defend, the attacker cannot spend Focus tokens or reroll attack dice.

fields.name: Hull Upgrade
fields.ai_description: Increase your Hull value by 1.

fields.name: Expose
fields.ai_description: Action: Until the end of the round, increase your primary weapon value by 1 and decrease your Agility value by 1. (Replaces Focus action.)

fields.name: Targeting Computer
fields.ai_description: After selecting a target, you may perform a free Target Lock action on it. Spend this Lock after attacking.

fields.name: Opportunist
fields.ai_description: While attacking, if you are not stressed and the defender is not focusing or evading, roll 1 additional attack die. Prioritize targets that trigger this ability.

fields.name: Turr Phennir
fields.ai_description: After you perform an attack, perform a free Boost or Barrel Roll action if doing so reduces the number of total possible attack dice threatening you.

fields.name: Push the Limit
fields.ai_description: Perform an additional action during Action Selection.

fields.name: Captain Kagi
fields.ai_description: When an enemy ship acquires a Target Lock, it must lock onto your ship if able.

fields.name: Soontir Fel
fields.ai_description: After selecting a target, gain 1 Focus token.

fields.name: Predator
fields.description: While you perform a primary attack, if the defender is in your Bullseye Arc, you may reroll 1 attack die.
fields.ai_description: While you perform a primary attack, if the defender is in your Bullseye Arc, you may reroll 1 attack die.

fields.name: Rexler Brath
fields.ai_description: When attacking, all Damage cards you deal to the defender are dealt face-up.

fields.name: Lone Wolf
fields.ai_description: When attacking or defending, if there re no other friendly ships at range 0-2, you may reroll 1 of your blank results.

fields.name: Mauler Mithel
fields.ai_description: When attacking at range 1, roll 1 additional attack die.

fields.name: Homing Missiles
fields.ai_description: Attack [Lock]: Spend 1 Charge. After you declare the defender, the defender may choose to suffer 1 Hit. If it does, skip the attack and Defense Dice steps and the attack is treated as hitting.

fields.name: Extra Munitions
fields.ai_description: Add one Charge to any equipped ordnance.

fields.name: Calculation
fields.ai_description: Gain a Calculate token. You may spend the token to change 1 of your Focus results to a Hit or Evade result.

fields.name: Lieutenant Colzet
fields.ai_description: After attacking, if you have a Target Lock on the defender, spend it to flip 1 random face-down Damage card assigned to the defender face-up.

fields.name: Skilled Bombardier
fields.description: If you would drop or launch a device, you may use a template of the same bearing with a speed 1 higher or lower.

fields.name: R4 Astromech
fields.description: Decrease the difficulty of your speed 1-2 basic maneuvers.

fields.name: Seismic Charges
fields.description: Bomb: During the system phase, you may spend 1 Charge to drop a Seismic Charge

fields.name: Agile Gunner
fields.description: During the End phase, you may rotate your Turret indicator
